</div><div title="cat-hiccups-why-do-they-happen-and-how-to-stop-them" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-hYQoXb ctGkmz pf-16_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-db77efd2--cathiccupswhydotheyhappenandhowtostopthem_1200x.jpg?v=1618080933" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0079/3287/0756/t/6/assets/pf-db77efd2--cathiccupswhydotheyhappenandhowtostopthem.jpg?v=1618080933 1536w" width="905" height="408" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="cat-hiccups-why-do-they-happen-and-how-to-stop-them" title="cat-hiccups-why-do-they-happen-and-how-to-stop-them"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-17_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bGaVxB jzqjUH pf-18_"><p class="sc-hGnimi ljiQdr pf-19_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-21_">Charles Osborne started hiccupping in 1922, and he didn't stop until 1990, that's 68 years and approximately 430 million hiccups later. He is the current Guinness World Record holder for the longest attack of hiccups.<br><br>We will explore the possibility of cat hiccups and find out if your cat is likely to break this record.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bGaVxB jzqjUH pf-22_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-ksHpcM hkPZIR pf-23_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jvvksu EHytM pf-24_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-26_">Table Of Contents</span></h3><p class="sc-hGnimi ljiQdr pf-27_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-29_"><a style="color: #00aaff;" href="#can-a-cat get hiccups">Can a cat get hiccups?</a><br>
